          We work with many other sectors. Contact us to discuss your specific needs and how AI can help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Schedule Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Learn About Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
